OL,3,CSurgeon admits fraud after having his
OL,4,Cown legs removed
OL,6,F***Warning: This article contains
OL,7,Fdetails some readers may find
OL,8,Fdistressing***
OL,10,FA vascular surgeon who carried out
OL,11,Fhundreds of amputation operations
OL,12,Fbefore having his own legs removed has
OL,13,Fadmitted fraud and possessing extreme
OL,14,Fpornography.
OL,16,FNeil Hopper, 49, pleaded guilty to two
OL,17,Fcharges of fraud by false
OL,18,Frepresentation relating to claims made
OL,19,Fto insurance companies that his legs
OL,20,Fhad been amputated due to illness
OL,21,Frather than self-inflicted injury.
