OL,6,FThe court heard he dishonestly
OL,7,Fobtained more than #466,000 from two
OL,8,Finsurance policies, telling the
OL,9,Finsurers he had 'flu-like symptoms'
OL,10,Fand 'septicaemia'.
OL,12,FHe spent the money on a camper van,
OL,13,Fprosthetics, building work, home
OL,14,Fimprovements, a hot tub and a wood
OL,15,Fburner.
OL,17,FThe court also heard that Hopper
OL,18,Fbought three 'extreme pornographic
OL,19,Fimages' online from Marius Gustavson.
OL,20,FThe videos showed people having body
OL,21,Fparts removed.
