OL,6,FDuring the court hearing on Thursday,
OL,7,FJudge James Adkin, the honorary
OL,8,Frecorder of Truro, heard Hopper was
OL,9,Fidentified following investigations
OL,10,Finto Marius Gustavson who ran the
OL,11,Fwebsite.
OL,13,FGustavson was jailed for life with a
OL,14,Fminimum term of 22 years at the Old
OL,15,FBailey last year for leading an
OL,16,Fextreme body modification ring.
OL,18,FHe netted more than #300,000 between
OL,19,F2017 and 2021 after posting videos of
OL,20,Fvarious procedures on his website.
