OL,6,FJudge's remarks on sentencing
OL,8,FJudge James Adkin imposed a jail
OL,9,Fsentence for a total of 32 months and
OL,10,Ftold Neil Hopper he would serve 40% in
OL,11,Fcustody before he could be considered
OL,12,Ffor parole.
OL,14,FHe was also made the subject of a
OL,15,FSexual Harm Prevention Order for 10
OL,16,Fyears.
