OL,6,F"You were in hospital for six weeks
OL,7,Fand after many tests and a variety of
OL,8,Ftreatments the medics decided your
OL,9,Ffeet could not be saved and they
OL,10,Famputated on May 17.
OL,12,F"You subsequently made fraudulent
OL,13,Finsurance claims to Aviva and Old
OL,14,FMutual Wealth receiving a total of
OL,15,F#466,000 fraudulently by representing
OL,16,Fthat the injuries were organic, caused
OL,17,Fby sepsis, when you caused the injury
OL,18,Fseemingly at least in part for sexual
OL,19,Fgratification."
