OL,6,FIn April 2019, Hopper decided to cause
OL,7,F"irreversible damage to his legs" when
OL,8,Fhis family were staying with his in
OL,9,Flaws.
OL,11,F"He knows in the days and weeks that
OL,12,Ffollowed, he let himself down in the
OL,13,Fmost shameful way," Mr Langdon said.
OL,15,FThe barrister said Hopper's wife
OL,16,Fwanted a divorce, he would probably
OL,17,Flose his home and he accepted that his
OL,18,Fmedical career was over.
