OL,6,FQuoting Hopper, he said: "My thoughts
OL,7,Fand behaviour have not have any effect
OL,8,Fon my job. I worked very hard and
OL,9,Falways tried my best for my patients."
OL,11,FHopper has not worked at the Royal
OL,12,FCornwall Hospitals NHS Trust since
OL,13,FMarch 2023.
OL,15,FThe General Medical Council placed
OL,16,Frestrictions on his practice the
