OL,6,F"While the details of the charges are
OL,7,Fshocking, it is important to stress
OL,8,Fthat the convictions do not relate to
OL,9,FMr Hopper's professional conduct.
OL,10,FDuring a thorough and painstaking
OL,11,Fpolice investigation there were no
OL,12,Flinks found to any patients he treated
OL,13,Fduring his work.
OL,15,F"Mr Hopper worked at the Royal
OL,16,FCornwall Hospitals from 2013 until he
OL,17,Fwas suspended from duty in March 2023,
OL,18,Fimmediately following his arrest.
